{"video_id": "cPLYxqZ1R28", "title": "Srimad Bhagavatam I Sri Satya Gaurachandra Dasa I SB 6.4.30 I 25.08.2022", "speaker": "HG Satya Gaura Chandra Dasa", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cPLYxqZ1R28", "duration": 1851, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 4.36, "text": " ओम्नमो बगवते वासुदेवाया"}, {"start": 4.36, "end": 13.46, "text": " रीडिंग फ्रम शेमत भागवतं कैन्टो सिक्स चैप्टर फोर टेक्स्ट थर्टी"}, {"start": 13.46, "end": 16.94, "text": " यस्मिन्यतो ये नचयस्य यस्मै"}, {"start": 16.94, "end": 23.68, "text": " यद्यो यथाकुरुते खार्यतेचा"}, {"start": 23.68, "end": 29.98, "text": " परावरेशाम परमंप्रागप्रसिद्धम"}, {"start": 29.98, "end": 36.38, "text": " तद्भ्रम्मतद्धेतुरनन्यधेकं"}, {"start": 36.38, "end": 39.42, "text": " तद्भ्रम्मतद्धेतुरनन्यधेकं"}, {"start": 39.42, "end": 43.92, "text": " परपोर्ट बाईस डिवाइन ग्रेस एसी बक्तविदान्त स्वामिष्य प्रोपाद"}, {"start": 43.92, "end": 59.96, "text": " तद्भ्रम्मतद्धेतुरनन्यधेकं"}, {"start": 59.980000000000004, "end": 66.38000000000001, "text": " He is the ultimate objective, and whether acting or causing others to act, He is the ultimate doer."}, {"start": 67.16, "end": 71.84, "text": " There are many causes, high and low, but since He is the cause of all causes,"}, {"start": 72.52000000000001, "end": 77.38000000000001, "text": " He is well known as the Supreme Brahman who existed before all activities."}, {"start": 77.38000000000001, "end": 81.62, "text": " He is one without a second, and has no other cause."}, {"start": 82.28, "end": 84.80000000000001, "text": " I therefore offer my respects unto Him."}, {"start": 84.8, "end": 94.46, "text": " The Supreme Personality of Godhead, Krishna, is the original cause, as confirmed in Bhagavad Gita,"}, {"start": 94.96, "end": 102.2, "text": " Even this material world, which is conducted under the modes of material nature,"}, {"start": 102.2, "end": 110.96, "text": " is caused by the Supreme Personality of Godhead, who therefore also has an intimate relationship with the material world."}, {"start": 111.64, "end": 114.78, "text": " If the material world were not a part of His body,"}, {"start": 114.8, "end": 119.8, "text": " the Supreme Lord, the Supreme Cause, would be incomplete."}, {"start": 120.42, "end": 121.72, "text": " Therefore, we hear,"}, {"start": 122.2, "end": 130.42, "text": " If one knows that Vasudeva is the original cause of all causes,"}, {"start": 130.9, "end": 132.98, "text": " He becomes a perfect Mahatma."}, {"start": 133.68, "end": 136.34, "text": " In the Brahma Samhita, it declares,"}, {"start": 136.96, "end": 140.26, "text": " Ishwara Paramakrishna, Sachidananda Vigraha,"}, {"start": 140.74, "end": 143.8, "text": " Anadiradir Govindaha Sarvakaranakaranam,"}, {"start": 144.8, "end": 148.72, "text": " Krishna, who is known as Govinda, is the Supreme Controller."}, {"start": 149.44, "end": 151.86, "text": " He has an eternal, blissful, spiritual body."}, {"start": 152.56, "end": 153.70000000000002, "text": " He is the origin of all."}, {"start": 154.3, "end": 159.10000000000002, "text": " He has no other origin, for He is the prime cause of all causes."}, {"start": 159.3, "end": 163.4, "text": " The Supreme Brahman, Tad Brahma, is the cause of all causes,"}, {"start": 163.82000000000002, "end": 165.28, "text": " but He has no cause."}, {"start": 165.52, "end": 169.18, "text": " Anadiradir Govinda Sarvakaranakaranam,"}, {"start": 169.9, "end": 172.66000000000003, "text": " Govinda Krishna is the original cause of all causes,"}, {"start": 173.14000000000001, "end": 174.36, "text": " but He has no cause."}, {"start": 174.8, "end": 176.8, "text": " For His appearance as Govinda,"}, {"start": 177.20000000000002, "end": 179.8, "text": " Govinda expands in multifarious forms,"}, {"start": 180.32000000000002, "end": 182.32000000000002, "text": " but nevertheless they are one,"}, {"start": 182.32000000000002, "end": 184.32000000000002, "text": " as confirmed by Madhavacharya."}, {"start": 186.32000000000002, "end": 192.8, "text": " Ananyaha sadrusha bhavad eko roopadi abhedatah"}, {"start": 193.36, "end": 196.8, "text": " Krishna has no cause, nor any equal,"}, {"start": 197.12, "end": 201.44, "text": " and He is one, because His various forms,"}, {"start": 201.44, "end": 203.44, "text": " as formsa and vibhannamsa,"}, {"start": 203.44, "end": 204.64000000000001, "text": " are non-different."}, {"start": 204.64000000000001, "end": 206.16000000000003, "text": " Different from Himself."}, {"start": 206.16000000000003, "end": 209.70000000000002, "text": " This is the Bhagavad Gita, parupottoma."}, {"start": 211.02, "end": 215.12, "text": " So recently, there was a news,"}, {"start": 215.12, "end": 218.24, "text": " an interesting article about"}, {"start": 218.24, "end": 224.32000000000002, "text": " a new tendency that is developing in the youngsters,"}, {"start": 224.32000000000002, "end": 228.32000000000002, "text": " not only youngsters even in the elders also,"}, {"start": 228.32000000000002, "end": 232.88000000000002, "text": " and they figured out that about"}, {"start": 232.88000000000002, "end": 234.08, "text": " ,"}, {"start": 234.64000000000001, "end": 247.64000000000001, "text": " 3% of Indian population are having these kind of tendencies, quite a big number. India is a very populous country."}, {"start": 249.64000000000001, "end": 251.64000000000001, "text": " Now what are those symptoms?"}, {"start": 251.64000000000001, "end": 268.64, "text": " The symptoms are connected to utilizing this social media, mobiles, laptops, gadgets, which give access to the social media."}, {"start": 271.64, "end": 280.64, "text": " A young man or a young girl, they take photographs."}, {"start": 282.64, "end": 286.64, "text": " And then they immediately upload it into the social media."}, {"start": 288.64, "end": 298.64, "text": " Nowadays they can take photographs of anything, any damn thing and put it up on the social media. There's somebody to see."}, {"start": 302.64, "end": 310.64, "text": " And then when a boy or a girl or anybody, say he takes a photograph of himself."}, {"start": 312.64, "end": 317.64, "text": " Or herself, and then post it on to the social media."}, {"start": 318.64, "end": 320.64, "text": " Then begins the tension."}, {"start": 322.64, "end": 328.64, "text": " How many, how many views, how many responded?"}, {"start": 329.64, "end": 332.64, "text": " Nowadays there are more options are there, you know, not only this and that."}, {"start": 333.64, "end": 336.64, "text": " We used to have only one, one this way, one this way."}, {"start": 338.64, "end": 340.64, "text": " Now it has changed, you know."}, {"start": 340.64, "end": 344.64, "text": " There are love symbols and so many other faces probably you can put up."}, {"start": 345.64, "end": 347.64, "text": " So, it's a tension."}, {"start": 348.64, "end": 351.64, "text": " How many people are liking it, how many are not liking it."}, {"start": 352.64, "end": 356.64, "text": " And imagine you say this is the best picture of myself and post it."}, {"start": 357.64, "end": 358.64, "text": " And nobody is responding."}, {"start": 359.64, "end": 361.64, "text": " There is a big silence."}, {"start": 362.64, "end": 365.64, "text": " So this is the anxiety people are going."}, {"start": 365.64, "end": 370.64, "text": " Recently it's very surprising in Hyderabad."}, {"start": 371.64, "end": 379.64, "text": " One young girl, she has committed suicide because her YouTube views are not increasing."}, {"start": 383.64, "end": 385.64, "text": " So it's a real problem."}, {"start": 387.64, "end": 388.64, "text": " It's a very big problem."}, {"start": 389.64, "end": 390.64, "text": " 3% of the population are having it."}, {"start": 390.64, "end": 395.64, "text": " So, scientists, of course as usual they got into the picture."}, {"start": 396.64, "end": 398.64, "text": " First thing they do is they will give a name."}, {"start": 399.64, "end": 401.64, "text": " They can't find any solutions."}, {"start": 402.64, "end": 405.64, "text": " But, they gave a name."}, {"start": 406.64, "end": 408.64, "text": " They call this as digital depression."}, {"start": 410.64, "end": 415.64, "text": " Previously, very near dear ones, say passes away."}, {"start": 416.64, "end": 418.64, "text": " Somebody used to get into depression."}, {"start": 418.64, "end": 421.64, "text": " So, depression has always been there."}, {"start": 422.64, "end": 425.64, "text": " But, this is a new depression that has been created."}, {"start": 426.64, "end": 428.64, "text": " A digital depression."}, {"start": 431.64, "end": 438.64, "text": " They have mentioned what are the symptoms of this depression."}, {"start": 441.64, "end": 445.64, "text": " One is they lose self-confidence."}, {"start": 446.64, "end": 447.64, "text": " Obviously, you know."}, {"start": 448.64, "end": 449.64, "text": " You know something."}, {"start": 450.64, "end": 454.64, "text": " And, you have put all your confidence in the hands of others."}, {"start": 456.64, "end": 458.64, "text": " Obviously, you will lose your own confidence."}, {"start": 459.64, "end": 463.64, "text": " And then, always they are in a lamenting mood."}, {"start": 464.64, "end": 465.64, "text": " Lamentation."}, {"start": 467.64, "end": 469.64, "text": " Then, concentration is disturbed."}, {"start": 471.64, "end": 473.64, "text": " Decision making power is affected."}, {"start": 475.64, "end": 476.64, "text": " Suicidal thoughts."}, {"start": 478.64, "end": 480.64, "text": " Then, lack of sleep."}, {"start": 481.64, "end": 482.64, "text": " Loneliness."}, {"start": 483.64, "end": 484.64, "text": " Weakness."}, {"start": 485.64, "end": 489.64, "text": " These are the symptoms that they have mentioned."}, {"start": 490.64, "end": 492.64, "text": " This is called digital depression."}, {"start": 493.64, "end": 496.64, "text": " There is a tsunami of depressed people in the world."}, {"start": 499.64, "end": 505.64, "text": " So, then they figured out some main reasons."}, {"start": 505.64, "end": 511.64, "text": " They are saying using this technology too much."}, {"start": 512.64, "end": 517.64, "text": " Spending too much time with laptops, gadgets and smart phones."}, {"start": 518.64, "end": 520.64, "text": " Not mixing with any friends."}, {"start": 521.64, "end": 524.64, "text": " Then, active participation in social media."}, {"start": 525.64, "end": 527.64, "text": " Responses."}, {"start": 528.64, "end": 532.64, "text": " They said if the social media has comment section."}, {"start": 532.64, "end": 536.64, "text": " 22% of the people are becoming sick."}, {"start": 537.64, "end": 539.64, "text": " Because, you will put some comment."}, {"start": 539.64, "end": 541.64, "text": " 100 people will pounce on you."}, {"start": 542.64, "end": 544.64, "text": " And then, you have to respond to each one."}, {"start": 545.64, "end": 546.64, "text": " And then, you know."}, {"start": 547.64, "end": 548.64, "text": " It's a different life."}, {"start": 551.64, "end": 554.64, "text": " So, they have mentioned some of these reasons."}, {"start": 555.64, "end": 557.64, "text": " And then, they also suggested some solutions."}, {"start": 559.64, "end": 561.64, "text": " Each of these causes, if you see."}, {"start": 561.64, "end": 564.64, "text": " What is the cause?"}, {"start": 565.64, "end": 568.64, "text": " Of course, they have mentioned some cause."}, {"start": 569.64, "end": 570.64, "text": " But, what is the cause?"}, {"start": 571.64, "end": 572.64, "text": " Is a loaded question."}, {"start": 575.64, "end": 577.64, "text": " The mankind has been discussing."}, {"start": 578.64, "end": 579.64, "text": " What is the cause?"}, {"start": 580.64, "end": 582.64, "text": " For human current situation."}, {"start": 583.64, "end": 585.64, "text": " That the humanity is in."}, {"start": 586.64, "end": 588.64, "text": " What is the cause?"}, {"start": 588.64, "end": 592.64, "text": " This has always been a question to big, big philosophers."}, {"start": 593.64, "end": 594.64, "text": " And big, big scientists."}, {"start": 595.64, "end": 596.64, "text": " What is the cause?"}, {"start": 597.64, "end": 600.64, "text": " Particularly, for our suffering and difficulties."}, {"start": 601.64, "end": 602.64, "text": " What is the cause?"}, {"start": 603.64, "end": 607.64, "text": " So, this verse addresses that."}, {"start": 608.64, "end": 610.64, "text": " What is the cause for all this?"}, {"start": 612.64, "end": 617.64, "text": " Once, we know this Parikshit Maharaj's pastime."}, {"start": 619.64, "end": 621.64, "text": " Of touring in the entire world."}, {"start": 624.64, "end": 627.64, "text": " And then, suddenly in one place he sees."}, {"start": 628.64, "end": 630.64, "text": " The Kalipurusha is beating."}, {"start": 631.64, "end": 634.64, "text": " The legs of the Dharma."}, {"start": 636.64, "end": 638.64, "text": " Legs of the cow."}, {"start": 640.64, "end": 643.64, "text": " And after some discussions, Parikshit Maharaj asks."}, {"start": 644.64, "end": 646.64, "text": " The personality of religion, bull."}, {"start": 646.64, "end": 648.64, "text": " He asks this question."}, {"start": 649.64, "end": 650.64, "text": " Tell me."}, {"start": 651.64, "end": 653.64, "text": " What is the source of your suffering?"}, {"start": 655.64, "end": 657.64, "text": " What is the cause of your suffering?"}, {"start": 658.64, "end": 661.64, "text": " Actually, everybody knows that Kali, that fellow is there."}, {"start": 664.64, "end": 666.64, "text": " But, when he asks this question."}, {"start": 667.64, "end": 668.64, "text": " Very interesting."}, {"start": 669.64, "end": 671.64, "text": " Bull, the personality of religion."}, {"start": 671.64, "end": 677.64, "text": " The bull, refuses to identify a cause."}, {"start": 678.64, "end": 680.64, "text": " It says."}, {"start": 682.64, "end": 692.64, "text": " Navayam kleshabhijhani yata syupurusharsabha purusham tam vijhanimo vakyabhedavimohita"}, {"start": 693.64, "end": 695.64, "text": " O greatest among human beings."}, {"start": 696.64, "end": 698.64, "text": " It is very difficult to ascertain."}, {"start": 698.64, "end": 700.64, "text": " The particular miscreant."}, {"start": 701.64, "end": 702.64, "text": " Who has caused our sufferings."}, {"start": 703.64, "end": 705.64, "text": " Actually, very clearly you can see."}, {"start": 705.64, "end": 706.64, "text": " That fellow is holding the."}, {"start": 707.64, "end": 708.64, "text": " You know, thing and then."}, {"start": 709.64, "end": 711.64, "text": " She is, then the bull is saying."}, {"start": 712.64, "end": 714.64, "text": " Because, we are bewildered by."}, {"start": 715.64, "end": 716.64, "text": " All the different opinions of."}, {"start": 717.64, "end": 719.64, "text": " Theoretical philosophers."}, {"start": 720.64, "end": 722.64, "text": " So, five thousand years ago also."}, {"start": 723.64, "end": 725.64, "text": " There is a, there are these so called philosophers."}, {"start": 726.64, "end": 727.64, "text": " Who bewilders."}, {"start": 727.64, "end": 728.64, "text": " By various."}, {"start": 729.64, "end": 730.64, "text": " Vakyabhedha."}, {"start": 731.64, "end": 732.64, "text": " Differing opinions on."}, {"start": 733.64, "end": 734.64, "text": " Why we are suffering."}, {"start": 736.64, "end": 737.64, "text": " What is the cause."}, {"start": 738.64, "end": 739.64, "text": " This is a very big question."}, {"start": 739.64, "end": 740.64, "text": " In everybody's mind."}, {"start": 742.64, "end": 743.64, "text": " Then."}, {"start": 744.64, "end": 745.64, "text": " The personified."}, {"start": 746.64, "end": 747.64, "text": " Religion."}, {"start": 747.64, "end": 748.64, "text": " Goes on to say."}, {"start": 749.64, "end": 751.64, "text": " Kecchid vikalpavasana."}, {"start": 752.64, "end": 754.64, "text": " Ahur atmanam atmanah."}, {"start": 754.64, "end": 757.64, "text": " Daivam anye pare karma."}, {"start": 758.64, "end": 759.64, "text": " Subhavam apare prabhum."}, {"start": 760.64, "end": 761.64, "text": " Now."}, {"start": 761.64, "end": 762.64, "text": " He starts listing down."}, {"start": 763.64, "end": 764.64, "text": " The various philosophies about."}, {"start": 765.64, "end": 766.64, "text": " What is the cause."}, {"start": 769.64, "end": 770.64, "text": " Trans, translation."}, {"start": 771.64, "end": 772.64, "text": " Some of the philosophers."}, {"start": 773.64, "end": 774.64, "text": " They deny."}, {"start": 774.64, "end": 775.64, "text": " All sorts of duality."}, {"start": 778.64, "end": 779.64, "text": " Duality means."}, {"start": 780.64, "end": 781.64, "text": " Good."}, {"start": 781.64, "end": 782.64, "text": " Bad."}, {"start": 782.64, "end": 783.64, "text": " Happiness."}, {"start": 783.64, "end": 784.64, "text": " Distress."}, {"start": 784.64, "end": 785.64, "text": " They deny."}, {"start": 787.64, "end": 788.64, "text": " They declare that."}, {"start": 788.64, "end": 789.64, "text": " One's own self."}, {"start": 789.64, "end": 790.64, "text": " Is responsible for."}, {"start": 791.64, "end": 792.64, "text": " His personal happiness."}, {"start": 792.64, "end": 793.64, "text": " And distress."}, {"start": 795.64, "end": 796.64, "text": " So they say."}, {"start": 796.64, "end": 797.64, "text": " Our own."}, {"start": 797.64, "end": 798.64, "text": " Fruit of activity."}, {"start": 799.64, "end": 800.64, "text": " Is a cause."}, {"start": 801.64, "end": 802.64, "text": " That's why you are suffering."}, {"start": 803.64, "end": 804.64, "text": " But the fruit of activity."}, {"start": 805.64, "end": 806.64, "text": " Will be done by somebody."}, {"start": 807.64, "end": 808.64, "text": " So yourself is a cause."}, {"start": 810.64, "end": 811.64, "text": " And then."}, {"start": 811.64, "end": 812.64, "text": " Others say that."}, {"start": 812.64, "end": 813.64, "text": " Superhuman powers."}, {"start": 813.64, "end": 814.64, "text": " Are responsible."}, {"start": 814.64, "end": 815.64, "text": " Demigods are."}, {"start": 815.64, "end": 816.64, "text": " Responsible."}, {"start": 816.64, "end": 817.64, "text": " We are not."}, {"start": 817.64, "end": 818.64, "text": " Demigods are."}, {"start": 818.64, "end": 819.64, "text": " Responsible."}, {"start": 820.64, "end": 821.64, "text": " Well."}, {"start": 821.64, "end": 822.64, "text": " Let others say."}, {"start": 822.64, "end": 823.64, "text": " That activity."}, {"start": 823.64, "end": 824.64, "text": " Is responsible."}, {"start": 824.64, "end": 825.64, "text": " One's own karma."}, {"start": 827.64, "end": 828.64, "text": " And the gross."}, {"start": 828.64, "end": 829.64, "text": " Materialists say."}, {"start": 829.64, "end": 830.64, "text": " That the nature."}, {"start": 830.64, "end": 831.64, "text": " Is the ultimate cause."}, {"start": 832.64, "end": 833.64, "text": " They say."}, {"start": 833.64, "end": 834.64, "text": " The nature."}, {"start": 834.64, "end": 835.64, "text": " Matter."}, {"start": 835.64, "end": 836.64, "text": " Is the cause."}, {"start": 836.64, "end": 837.64, "text": " Nature means."}, {"start": 837.64, "end": 838.64, "text": " They see."}, {"start": 838.64, "end": 839.64, "text": " The matter around."}, {"start": 839.64, "end": 840.64, "text": " So this is."}, {"start": 840.64, "end": 841.64, "text": " A big discussion."}, {"start": 841.64, "end": 842.64, "text": " With the scientific."}, {"start": 842.64, "end": 843.64, "text": " Community."}, {"start": 843.64, "end": 844.64, "text": " How."}, {"start": 844.64, "end": 845.64, "text": " Did."}, {"start": 845.64, "end": 846.64, "text": " This world."}, {"start": 846.64, "end": 847.64, "text": " Come into picture."}, {"start": 847.64, "end": 848.64, "text": " And what."}, {"start": 848.64, "end": 849.64, "text": " Is the cause."}, {"start": 850.64, "end": 851.64, "text": " So."}, {"start": 851.64, "end": 852.64, "text": " Many of them."}, {"start": 852.64, "end": 853.64, "text": " Believe."}, {"start": 853.64, "end": 854.64, "text": " That the matter."}, {"start": 854.64, "end": 855.64, "text": " Is the cause."}, {"start": 855.64, "end": 856.64, "text": " As a material."}, {"start": 856.64, "end": 857.64, "text": " Nature."}, {"start": 857.64, "end": 858.64, "text": " Is the cause."}, {"start": 860.64, "end": 861.64, "text": " When."}, {"start": 861.64, "end": 862.64, "text": " I think."}, {"start": 862.64, "end": 863.64, "text": " Many years."}, {"start": 863.64, "end": 864.64, "text": " Back."}, {"start": 864.64, "end": 865.64, "text": " When."}, {"start": 865.64, "end": 866.64, "text": " They found."}, {"start": 866.64, "end": 867.64, "text": " One particle."}, {"start": 867.64, "end": 868.64, "text": " One extra."}, {"start": 868.64, "end": 869.64, "text": " Particle."}, {"start": 869.64, "end": 870.64, "text": " Inside."}, {"start": 870.64, "end": 871.64, "text": " The atom."}, {"start": 871.64, "end": 872.64, "text": " They named."}, {"start": 872.64, "end": 873.64, "text": " It."}, {"start": 873.64, "end": 874.64, "text": " As."}, {"start": 874.64, "end": 875.64, "text": " God."}, {"start": 875.64, "end": 876.64, "text": " Particle."}, {"start": 876.64, "end": 877.64, "text": " So."}, {"start": 877.64, "end": 878.64, "text": " Everybody."}, {"start": 878.64, "end": 879.64, "text": " Got."}, {"start": 879.64, "end": 880.64, "text": " Excited."}, {"start": 880.64, "end": 881.64, "text": " It's."}, {"start": 881.64, "end": 882.64, "text": " Only."}, {"start": 882.64, "end": 883.64, "text": " Name."}, {"start": 883.64, "end": 884.64, "text": " Otherwise."}, {"start": 884.64, "end": 885.64, "text": " There."}, {"start": 885.64, "end": 886.64, "text": " Is."}, {"start": 886.64, "end": 887.64, "text": " No."}, {"start": 887.64, "end": 888.64, "text": " It."}, {"start": 888.64, "end": 889.64, "text": " Has."}, {"start": 889.64, "end": 890.64, "text": " Not."}, {"start": 890.64, "end": 891.64, "text":